## 3. Technology Stack

| Layer | Choice | Rationale |
|-------|--------|-----------|
| **Framework** | React 18 + TypeScript | Component-based, type-safe |
| **Build Tool** | Vite | Fast HMR, modern bundling |
| **Routing** | React Router v6 | Client-side navigation |
| **State** | React Context + useReducer | Sufficient for local-first app |
| **Data Storage** | IndexedDB (via Dexie.js) | Multi-user, large dataset support, fully client-side |
| **Charts** | Recharts | React-native charting library |
| **Body Map** | Custom SVG component | Interactive, clickable muscle regions |
| **Styling** | Vanilla CSS (CSS Variables + Modules) | Full control, premium design |
| **Icons** | Lucide React | Clean, consistent icon set |

> [!NOTE]
> All data lives in the browser (IndexedDB). No back-end server is needed. Multi-user is achieved by user accounts stored locally — each user sees only their own data.

---

## 4. Data Models

### 4.1 User

| Field | Type | Description |
|-------|------|-------------|
| `id` | string (uuid) | Primary key |
| `username` | string | Unique login name |
| `password` | string (hashed) | Auth credential |
| `displayName` | string | Shown in UI |
| `avatarColor` | string | Profile color |
| `weight` | number | In kg |
| `height` | number | In cm |
| `age` | number | Years |
| `dailyCalorieGoal` | number | kcal target |
| `createdAt` | Date | Account creation |

### 4.2 Exercise (Database Entry)

| Field | Type | Description |
|-------|------|-------------|
| `id` | string | Primary key |
| `name` | string | e.g. "Bench Press" |
| `category` | enum | `strength` / `cardio` / `bodyweight` |
| `muscleGroups` | string[] | `["chest", "triceps", "front_delts"]` |
| `isCustom` | boolean | User-created or built-in |

### 4.3 Workout Session

| Field | Type | Description |
|-------|------|-------------|
| `id` | string | Primary key |
| `userId` | string | Owner |
| `date` | Date | When |
| `title` | string | e.g. "Push Day" |
| `duration` | number | Minutes |
| `entries` | WorkoutEntry[] | Exercises performed |
| `notes` | string | Optional |

### 4.4 WorkoutEntry

| Field | Type | Description |
|-------|------|-------------|
| `exerciseId` | string | Ref to Exercise |
| `sets` | SetData[] | For strength: `{ reps, weight }` |
| `duration` | number | For cardio: minutes |
| `distance` | number | For cardio: km |
| `caloriesBurned` | number | Estimated |

### 4.5 Food Item

| Field | Type | Description |
|-------|------|-------------|
| `id` | string | Primary key |
| `name` | string | e.g. "Chicken Breast" |
| `caloriesPer100g` | number | kcal |
| `proteinPer100g` | number | grams |
| `carbsPer100g` | number | grams |
| `fatPer100g` | number | grams |
| `isCustom` | boolean | User-created or built-in |

### 4.6 Meal Entry

| Field | Type | Description |
|-------|------|-------------|
| `id` | string | Primary key |
| `userId` | string | Owner |
| `date` | Date | When |
| `mealType` | enum | `breakfast` / `lunch` / `dinner` / `snack` |
| `foodItemId` | string | Ref to Food Item |
| `quantity` | number | grams |
| `calories` | number | Calculated |
| `protein` | number | Calculated |
| `carbs` | number | Calculated |
| `fat` | number | Calculated |

