## 7. UI Design Direction

### Color Palette (Dark Theme)

| Token | Value | Usage |
|-------|-------|-------|
| `--bg-primary` | `#0a0e1a` | App background |
| `--bg-surface` | `#141929` | Cards, panels |
| `--bg-elevated` | `#1c2137` | Modals, dropdowns |
| `--accent-primary` | `#6c63ff` | Primary actions, active states |
| `--accent-secondary` | `#00d9ff` | Secondary highlights |
| `--accent-success` | `#00e676` | Positive metrics |
| `--accent-warning` | `#ffab40` | Warnings, caution |
| `--accent-danger` | `#ff5252` | Errors, destructive |
| `--text-primary` | `#e8eaf6` | Main text |
| `--text-secondary` | `#7986cb` | Muted text |

### Design Features

- **Glassmorphism** cards with subtle backdrop-blur
- **Gradient accents** on key interactive elements
- **Smooth micro-animations** (page transitions, hover states, chart entry animations)
- **Modern typography** — Inter font from Google Fonts
- **Responsive layout** — sidebar collapses on mobile

