## 8. Built-in Exercise & Food Databases

### Pre-loaded Exercises (50+)

The app ships with a comprehensive exercise database. Examples:

| Exercise | Category | Muscle Groups |
|----------|----------|---------------|
| Bench Press | Strength | Chest, Triceps, Front Delts |
| Squat | Strength | Quads, Glutes, Hamstrings |
| Deadlift | Strength | Back, Glutes, Hamstrings |
| Pull-Up | Strength | Lats, Biceps |
| Running | Cardio | Quads, Calves, Hamstrings |
| Cycling | Cardio | Quads, Calves |
| Plank | Bodyweight | Abs, Obliques |
| ... | ... | ... |

### Pre-loaded Foods (50+)

| Food | Cal/100g | Protein | Carbs | Fat |
|------|----------|---------|-------|-----|
| Chicken Breast | 165 | 31g | 0g | 3.6g |
| Brown Rice | 112 | 2.3g | 24g | 0.8g |
| Egg (whole) | 155 | 13g | 1.1g | 11g |
| Banana | 89 | 1.1g | 23g | 0.3g |
| ... | ... | ... | ... | ... |

Users can also add custom exercises and foods.

